.TH rom-weaver 1  "rom-weaver 0.5.0"
.SH NAME
rom\-weaver \- Inspect, extract, checksum, compress, trim, and patch ROMs and disc images
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBrom\-weaver\fR [\fB\-\-json\fR] [\fB\-\-progress\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-progress\fR] [\fB\-\-log\-level\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR]... [\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR] [\fB\-\-dep\-trace\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Inspect, extract, checksum, compress, trim, and patch ROMs and disc images
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-json\fR
Emit progress and terminal status as JSON lines
.TP
\fB\-\-progress\fR
Force running progress events on
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-progress\fR
Disable running progress events
.TP
\fB\-\-log\-level\fR \fI<LOG_LEVEL>\fR
Set application log level (off, error, warn, info, debug, trace)
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
off
.IP \(bu 2
error
.IP \(bu 2
warn
.IP \(bu 2
info
.IP \(bu 2
debug
.IP \(bu 2
trace
.RE
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Increase application log verbosity; repeat for debug and trace
.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Show only application errors
.TP
\fB\-\-dep\-trace\fR
Enable trace logs from dependencies (for example nod)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
rom\-weaver\-probe(1)
Identify containers, patches, and known ROM headers
.TP
rom\-weaver\-extract(1)
Extract files and disc payloads from supported containers
.TP
rom\-weaver\-checksum(1)
Compute checksums for files or selected container payloads
.TP
rom\-weaver\-ingest(1)
Classify a source as ROM or patch, extracting nested containers and checksumming ROMs
.TP
rom\-weaver\-compress(1)
Create a supported archive or disc\-image container
.TP
rom\-weaver\-trim(1)
Trim or restore supported ROM and disc\-image formats
.TP
rom\-weaver\-patch(1)
Apply, create, or validate ROM patches
.TP
rom\-weaver\-bundle(1)
Create and parse rom\-weaver\-bundle.json workflows
.TP
rom\-weaver\-tools(1)
Run specialized recovery and conversion tools
.SH VERSION
v0.5.0
